bile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3611822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 27, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aau1665702621803.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aau1665702621803.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aau1665702621803.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aau1665702621803\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt;</span> constant determines how component state is managed for the server page or session service.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"aau1665702621803__topic_d93608e1_d93609e1_d93610e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aau1665702621803__p_d93611e1_d93612e1_d93613e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt;</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"aau1665702621803__section_w2773ab1b7b3_w2774ab1b7_w2775ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10301e1_d10302e1_d10303e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Technical Name:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n                        \n                        &lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Expected Value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code> |\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default Value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"aau1665702621803__section_w2776ab1b7b5_w2777ab1b7_w2778ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__2\">Component state is not managed using cookies or\n                        the state management component.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__2\">Component state is managed using\n                        cookies.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aau1665702621803__table_d10304e1_d10305e1_d10306e1__entry__2\">Component state is managed using the state\n                        management component (USYSSTAT).</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aau1665702621803__section_h51_t12_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d275531e185\">Scope</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aau1665702621803__p_d93617e1_d93618e1_d93619e1\">Dynamic server pages, static server pages, and session\n            services.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aau1665702621803__p_d93620e1_d93621e1_d93622e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$cmpStateManagedBy&gt;</span>\n            constant only in the preActivate and postActivate triggers.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aau1665702621803__section_oyj_v12_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d275531e200\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aau1665702621803__p_d93626e1_d93627e1_d93628e1\">The value of this constant is taken from the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">State Managed By</span> property of the component.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aau1665702621803__p_d93629e1_d93630e1_d93631e1\">In dynamic and static server pages, predefined code in\n            the preActivate and postActivate makes used of this constant.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aau1665702621803__section_ljm_bb2_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d275531e216\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"aau1665702621803__ul_tvn_db2_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aau1665702621803__li_d36482e1_d36483e1_d36484e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cdy1665702688628.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cdy1665702688628.html\" title=\"A Dynamic Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that can be incrementally and dynamically updated at runtime.\">Dynamic Server Page</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aau1665702621803__li_d36485e1_d36486e1_d36487e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jmi1665702688698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jmi1665702688698.html\" title=\"A Static Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that is updated as a complete page at runtime.\">Static Server Page</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aau1665702621803__li_d36488e1_d36489e1_d36490e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhd1665702582378.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhd1665702582378.html\" title=\"A Session Service is a Component that defines a business logic component for handling task-specific data processing for other components.\">Session Service</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cik1665702689127.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>State Managed By</a><p>Sets the value of the &lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt; constant, which specifies the mechanism used to save state information for the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vif1719486836379.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>State Management Mechanisms</a><p>The stateless nature of the HTTP protocol means that Uniface server pages are stateless and must explicitly implement state management using one or more of the available state management mechanisms.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nag1665702668833.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>USYSSTAT</a><p>USYSSTAT is a Uniface component that provides operations for managing component state in a temporary table. It can be used as-is, or as a starting point or template for creating your own state management mechanism.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "<$cmpStateManagedBy> Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 27, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The <$cmpStatemanagedBy> constant determines how component state is managed for the server page or session service. <$cmpStatemanagedBy> Technical Name: <$cmpStatemanagedBy> Expected Value: 0 | 1 | 2 Default Value: 0 Table 1. Values Value Description 0 Component state is not managed using cookies or the state management component. 1 Component state is managed using cookies. 2 Component state is managed using the state management component (USYSSTAT). Scope Dynamic server pages, static server pages, and session services. Use the <$cmpStateManagedBy> constant only in the preActivate and postActivate triggers. Description The value of this constant is taken from the State Managed By property of the component. In dynamic and static server pages, predefined code in the preActivate and postActivate makes used of this constant. Applies To Dynamic Server Page Static Server Page Session Service Related Links State Managed By Sets the value of the <$cmpStatemanagedBy> constant, which specifies the mechanism used to save state information for the component. State Management Mechanisms The stateless nature of the HTTP protocol means that Uniface server pages are stateless and must explicitly implement state management using one or more of the available state management mechanisms. USYSSTAT USYSSTAT is a Uniface component that provides operations for managing component state in a temporary table. It can be used as-is, or as a starting point or template for creating your own state management mechanism. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}